					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8067780#post-4063977</guid>
				<title>How to Contain SCP-4114</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8067780/scp-4114#post-4063977</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 20 Nov 2018 23:36:52 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Tommy Maxwell</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4871782</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Not many things exist when containing something like this, but here are 4 ways she can be contained:<br /> Contained:<br /> Shove her into SCP-106<br /> Alive:<br /> Get her to enter SCP-439<br /> Know where she is:<br /> Don't container her; use SCP-291 to swap her brain out with a suitable foundation agent. It will take 30 minutes to do this, she was asleep for 90.</p> <p>If it has to be a straitjacket, use SCP-438</p> <p>PS Love this SCP +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
